{"tid":2492769,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傳28歲警打中国疫苗後去世 家人遭威脅噤聲","createTime":"2021-04-17T11:07:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-17T11:39:28.000Z","uid":184679,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"211c54eab25e9574ea65eab2bd72065c291eda90","tid":2492769,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T11:07:49.000Z","msg":"最近網上不斷曝出接種國產疫苗死亡案例。最新傳出的一例是一名28歲的邊檢警察，接種國產疫苗後死亡，家屬遭威脅噤聲。<br />\n<br />\n大陸微博帳號「山下花野子」最早於4月10日發帖稱，自己的弟弟是一名邊檢警察，不到30歲，發病前身體健康，接種滅活疫苗後，突發血小板為零，腦出血、皮下出血等症狀，已在ICU昏迷17天，情況已報告國家疾控。<br />\n<br />\n貼文說，目前聯繫有臨床經驗的專家，無論是國內還是國外專家，都請和其家人聯繫，家屬需要更有效的治療方案。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images1.epochhk.com/pictures/194748/2@1200x1200.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages1.epochhk.com%2Fpictures%2F194748%2F2%401200x1200.jpg&h=6142fa35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n隨後，「山下花野子」又發貼文稱：「已聯繫到相關專家，謝謝好心人，相信奇蹟出現」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images1.epochhk.com/pictures/194749/3@1200x1200.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages1.epochhk.com%2Fpictures%2F194749%2F3%401200x1200.jpg&h=eb777792&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4月15日下午，「山下花野子」再度發微博說，弟弟今年28歲，是一名軍人，沒有病史。今年1月，單位統一安排接種國藥集團的北生滅活疫苗。第一針1月11日接種，第二針2月8日在深圳濱河大道婦幼社康中心接種。<br />\n<br />\n期間弟弟出現疲勞、皮下出血、牙齦出血的情況，到3月24日頭痛以為感冒，突發腦出血入院，4月15日去世。<br />\n<br />\n「山下花野子」質問，弟弟是「重度再障引起的腦出血，為什麼接種疫苗會引起再生障礙性貧血？請你們給家屬一個交代！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images1.epochhk.com/pictures/194750/3@1200x1200.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages1.epochhk.com%2Fpictures%2F194750%2F3%401200x1200.jpg&h=8c1119f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「山下花野子」發出另一則貼文顯示，她被威脅刪貼。<br />\n<br />\n她說，15日下午接到弟弟單位領導以及福田衛生健康局的電話，「希望我注意影響，然後沒有告知我的情況下封禁我的發言？」<br />\n<br />\n她表示，「一我沒有造謠，二我作為家屬提出疑問，需要解答，我沒有要與國家政府作對，我要給弟弟討個公道，一個人好好的人到底是怎麼沒的？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images1.epochhk.com/pictures/194751/4@1200x1200.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages1.epochhk.com%2Fpictures%2F194751%2F4%401200x1200.jpg&h=085828da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「山下花野子」的其中一條貼文在短短一天內就有7萬多人閱讀，但隔天再打開她的微博，發現有關她弟弟打疫苗去世的帖文已經全部被刪除。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2021-04-17/3156185\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.epochtimes.com%2Fnews%2F2021-04-17%2F3156185&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CL3ocbXMCqCW%2BK0Nx6tfHLyc%3D&h=c1441ab8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2021-04-17/3156185</a>"},{"pid":"d43e6ac808455292d6781d80f5959d87cfcd0cc0","tid":2492769,"uid":76310,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T11:09:01.000Z","msg":"放心, 777唔會令大家失望, 好快到大家"},{"pid":"dd22489bf551210f8a848b16383e9b33e21b1549","tid":2492769,"uid":228955,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T11:10:00.000Z","msg":"絕對唔出奇符合國情"},{"pid":"fb3b8b685a4d056ec8d3d8e87028638b4244e47b","tid":2492769,"uid":9998,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T11:11:27.000Z","msg":"我沒有要與國家政府作對，我要給弟弟討個公道 &lt;&lt;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢都kai既 討公道咪姐係作對"},{"pid":"6f3aa276283a4f6565187768f57cb3eff076370d","tid":2492769,"uid":277186,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T11:12:12.000Z","msg":"軍人為國捐軀 正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37041e164dda27b4ceca2a5b4dcb67f1036932e1","tid":2492769,"uid":36612,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T11:12:55.000Z","msg":"今次真係滅活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa4215b1215fbd954b67ca0ecb865214c3a1b91e","tid":2492769,"uid":59283,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T11:13:29.000Z","msg":"點解唔係3萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b297883a35caeb2e2da3d1e9826fea6dbc773ce3","tid":2492769,"uid":32968,"like":1,"disli